ESRI_ItemInformation.description:
Vector file (Polygon) representing Sedgwick Reserve boundary. Produced by Bill Kuhn (UCSB BIogeography Lab) walking the property fenceline with handheld GPS unit. 10% of fenceline that was difficult to access by foot was added using 1993 digital orthophoto. This is not a legal boundary for the reserve but can be used to show the general extent and location of Sedgwick Reserve.

This dataset was uploaded to Data Basin and is available with additional information at: /datasets/41b4381f2d0342d787cbc60bbcfae53a
